    Tissue name and tissue id mapping of GTEx V7.

    tissueSiteDetailGTExv7.Rd

    A dataset containing the 53 tissues' name and corresponding ID of GTEx V7.

    Format

    A data frame with 53 rows and 2 variables:

    tissueSiteDetail

    character string, tissue name

    tissueSiteDetailId

    character string, tissue id removding special character

    tissueSite

    character string, whole tissue name

    colorHex

    character string, color of the tissue in GTEx
